# VELOR Root Environment Example
#
# This repository uses separate configuration templates for backend and frontend services.
# Please copy and configure the respective environment templates:
#
#   Backend:  backend/.env.example (or backend/.env.verification.example) -> backend/.env
#   Frontend: frontend/.env.example (or frontend/.env.verification.example) -> frontend/.env
#
# Do not commit live credentials or .env files to source control.
